<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1190' id='t-1190'>This is a map of New York State</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='2875' id='t-2875'>that was made in 1937
by the General Drafting Company.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='6417' id='t-6417'>It's an extremely famous map
among cartography nerds,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='9938' id='t-9938'>because down here at the bottom
of the Catskill Mountains,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12683' id='t-12683'>there is a little town called Roscoe --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='14586' id='t-14586'>actually, this will go easier
if I just put it up here --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='17308' id='t-17308'>There's Roscoe, and then right
above Roscoe is Rockland, New York,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='20862' id='t-20862'>and then right above that
