</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='109072' id='t-109072'>It had a gas station, a general store,
