</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='112477' id='t-112477'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='115596' id='t-115596'>And this is of course a completely
irresistible metaphor to a novelist,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='120098' id='t-120098'>because we would all like to believe
