<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='235898' id='t-235898'>they'd threaten me with this
&quot;going on [my] permanent record,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='238851' id='t-238851'>or &quot;You'll never get a good job.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='241084' id='t-241084'>I didn't want a good job!</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243003' id='t-243003'>As far as I could tell at eleven
or twelve years old,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='245623' id='t-245623'>like, people with good jobs woke up
