</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='248799' id='t-248799'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='250828' id='t-250828'>and the men who had good jobs,
one of the first things they did</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='255424' id='t-255424'>was tie a strangulation item
