<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='276824' id='t-276824'>they can't possibly be happy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='278608' id='t-278608'>Why would I want to jump
over all of these hurdles</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='281044' id='t-281044'>and have that be the end?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='283068' id='t-283068'>That's a terrible end!</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='285454' id='t-285454'>And then, when I was in tenth grade,
I went to this school,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='288656' id='t-288656'>Indian Springs School,
a small boarding school,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='291442' id='t-291442'>outside of Birmingham, Alabama.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='293276' id='t-293276'>And all at once I became a learner.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='296815' id='t-296815'>And I became a learner,
because I found myself</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='299035' id='t-299035'>in a community of learners.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='301083' id='t-301083'>I found myself surrounded by people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='302870' id='t-302870'>who celebrated intellectualism
and engagement,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='306124' id='t-306124'>and who thought that my ironic
oh-so-cool disengagement</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='310321' id='t-310321'>wasn't clever, or funny,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='312199' id='t-312199'>but, like, it was a simple
and unspectacular response</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='315985' id='t-315985'>to very complicated
and compelling problems.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='318692' id='t-318692'>And so I started to learn,
because learning was cool.</span>
